Why these terms exist: ARC Chain is 99,000+ lines of original Rust
built from scratch by a solo founder. These terms exist to prevent
the code from being forked and repackaged as someone else's chain.
If you want to build on ARC, you have unlimited freedom. If you want
to take the code and launch your own chain, talk to us first. We
would rather work with you than against you. Reach out: tj@arc.ai

